The *Backup File Prefix* under the "Daily Backup Admin" section is a mandatory field, at the moment, irrespective of the "Daily Backup" feature being turned *OFF*.
When backup has been turned *OFF*, and deleting the prefix, Confluence still prompts the user to specify a file prefix.

The prefix value should be ignored if the feature has been turned *OFF*.

